WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.710
Merry Christmas, everybody! Praise the

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:05.950
Lord. Day 64. I have Diana here with me

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:07.470
today, and we just wanted to come on

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:10.470
today and tell you all Merry

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:13.870
Christmas. We

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:15.829
love you all so much. Thank you for your

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:19.710
support. We appreciate all of

00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:19.720
you coming

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.029
out every day to these

00:00:22.039 --> 00:00:25.429
videos to pray with us and

00:00:25.439 --> 00:00:28.990
intercede for the nations.

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:33.750
Your support and love are so appreciated—praying for

00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.270
my daughter, for our family,

00:00:36.270 --> 00:00:36.280
and

00:00:36.280 --> 00:00:39.229
for me. The

00:00:39.239 --> 00:00:42.029
emails have been so kind lately, and

00:00:42.029 --> 00:00:42.039
I

00:00:42.039 --> 00:00:44.470
love the people sending

00:00:44.470 --> 00:00:44.480
earmuffs

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:47.150
for Megan for the sound.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:49.709
A lot of times she won't wear those

00:00:51.719 --> 00:00:52.990
because she doesn't like things on

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.110
her head, but we're getting there.

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:56.310
We're just believing God she's going

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.750
to be completely healed

00:00:57.750 --> 00:00:57.760
in

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.750
2024. We're closing this

00:00:59.760 --> 00:01:01.389
thing out, believing for the

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:03.910
complete manifestation of Megan.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.710
She holds her ears like that throughout the day. For all of you who are so considerate, I know you're doing it out of love. It's just a

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:15.230
habit, I think. Of

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.310
course, the earmuffs are so nice, so

00:01:17.310 --> 00:01:17.320
we're

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:19.230
going to try them.

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:20.390
Sometimes you wonder if it was just the

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.149
brand that she hasn't liked in

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:24.270
the past, so she'll wear

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:26.710
them for short periods.

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.990
Thank you all for helping my Megan out.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:32.429
What a blessing!

00:01:32.439 --> 00:01:34.270
So many people reaching out and

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:35.990
trying to help. I just wanted

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.990
to say thank you that you care.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.190
There are just a

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:42.350
lot of kind, wonderful people on here

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:45.469
with such

00:01:45.479 --> 00:01:49.069
great hearts. Thank you.

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:50.789
I believe the best is yet to

00:01:50.799 --> 00:01:54.270
come. 2025 is coming and I'm

00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:56.389
anticipating great things.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.789
We want to show you this real quick.

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:04.870
My wife went to the grocery store and

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:07.389
got this cake. It's

00:02:07.399 --> 00:02:08.990
green, so I don't want it to disappear behind

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:12.030
the green screen, but it says 'Happy

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:14.910
Birthday Jesus.'We try every year to

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.869
throw Jesus a birthday party

00:02:16.869 --> 00:02:16.879
with

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:19.430
brownies or cookies,

00:02:19.430 --> 00:02:19.440
and

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.949
this year Diana found a 'Happy

00:02:21.959 --> 00:02:24.229
Birthday Jesus'cake from the grocery

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:26.550
store.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:28.229
It

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.869
even

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:33.229
has a

00:02:33.239 --> 00:02:35.350
manger on it.

00:02:37.959 --> 00:02:39.910
We'll

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:43.070
sing happy birthday to Him as a family

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:45.270
and do a full-blown birthday party for

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:48.030
Him. He

00:02:48.030 --> 00:02:48.040
is

00:02:48.040 --> 00:02:49.990
our Lord and Savior. We wanted

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.470
to come on and tell you all a

00:02:52.470 --> 00:02:52.480
very

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:54.550
Merry Christmas. We're going

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.470
to take communion with you, so if you

00:02:56.480 --> 00:02:58.550
want to get your communion ready, we're

00:02:58.560 --> 00:02:59.830
going to

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.270
lift up the name of

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:05.110
Jesus. Let's lift up the body.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:08.470
His body was broken

00:03:08.470 --> 00:03:08.480
and

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:10.910
beaten for all our

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:13.070
transgressions and iniquities. The

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:15.309
chastisement of our peace was upon Him,

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:18.630
and with His stripes, you're healed.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:21.110
In this Christmas season, it's

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:24.190
even more of a gift to

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:26.589
believe for your divine healing and to

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:29.229
believe that everything

00:03:29.239 --> 00:03:31.509
broken in your body has

00:03:31.519 --> 00:03:34.470
been healed and made whole by

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:37.070
His stripes. No matter what it is,

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:39.309
nothing's too big and nothing's too

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:42.830
small. Jesus paid the price for it all.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.390
According to Galatians, Christ has

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:47.589
redeemed

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:49.589
us from the curse of the law, and the

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:50.910
curse of the law is everything in

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:54.949
Deuteronomy 28. I believe that Jesus

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:57.390
Christ is the same yesterday, today, and

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:59.789
forever, and that all things are possible

00:03:59.799 --> 00:04:01.990
to him who believes.

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.910
This beautiful Christmas

00:04:04.920 --> 00:04:07.190
day, where all the gifts are being poured

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:10.830
out on loved ones,

00:04:10.840 --> 00:04:14.030
Jesus gave the gift of His life.

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:17.550
He came as a child born in a manger

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:20.229
and wrapped in swaddling

00:04:20.239 --> 00:04:24.390
clothes as a gift for

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:28.189
humanity.

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:31.350
He died for every

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:33.390
single one of us so that we don't have to

00:04:33.400 --> 00:04:35.950
have all the bondage of this

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:39.749
earth. He came to set the captives free. The

00:04:39.749 --> 00:04:39.759
angels sang,

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.870
'Glory to God

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:44.909
in the highest, peace on earth,

00:04:44.909 --> 00:04:44.919
goodwill

00:04:44.919 --> 00:04:48.950
to

00:04:48.950 --> 00:04:48.960
men.'Hallelujah,

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:52.070
because of what He did on this very

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:55.390
special day, Jesus

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:58.510
paid the price. He lived 33

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:01.029
years and died on the cross after He was

00:05:01.039 --> 00:05:04.550
born. Oh, what a plan!

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:06.670
What an

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:09.990
amazing God we serve. He came to set the

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:14.189
captives free and

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:16.909
gave the ultimate sacrifice.

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:23.029
Thank you, Father, for giving Your Son.

00:05:23.039 --> 00:05:25.390
Thank you, Lord, for this body that was

00:05:25.400 --> 00:05:28.150
broken and beaten for us. Thank you

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:30.230
for communion,

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:32.629
that we are joint-heirs with You and

00:05:32.639 --> 00:05:34.909
we're able to be seated with You in the

00:05:34.919 --> 00:05:37.870
heavenlies, far above all principalities,

00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:40.909
powers, and might. We have dominion

00:05:40.919 --> 00:05:45.029
and authority over all satanic

00:05:45.029 --> 00:05:45.039
agendas.

00:05:45.039 --> 00:05:46.710
Father, I thank You that You

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:49.990
said nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.189
We take this body right now in the

00:05:52.199 --> 00:05:54.909
name of Jesus and we say, 'Happy Birthday,

00:05:54.909 --> 00:05:54.919
Jesus.'Thank

00:05:54.919 --> 00:05:57.950
You for this communion

00:05:57.950 --> 00:05:57.960
and

00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:00.350
for what You did for us. Thank You

00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:03.230
for coming to this earth as a baby.

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:07.790
We don't have to be bound by sickness

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.950
anymore.

00:06:20.599 --> 00:06:23.189
Now,

00:06:23.199 --> 00:06:26.749
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:06:28.319 --> 00:06:30.629
You said it

00:06:30.639 --> 00:06:34.070
was the cleansing flow that washed us

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:37.830
as white as snow. It took

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:40.830
care of all that sin and You made us

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:44.110
spotless before You. Father, we thank You

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:46.629
for that beautiful blood that flowed on

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:49.309
Calvary's tree. It flowed down and

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:52.189
cleansed Diana and me, and it cleansed

00:06:52.199 --> 00:06:54.270
every single one of you. We're so

00:06:54.280 --> 00:06:56.390
grateful for Your life and Your blood.

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:58.390
We thank You,

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:01.150
Lord, that as we confess our sins, You are

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:03.070
faithful and just to forgive us

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:06.550
and cleanse us from all

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.950
unrighteousness. He's

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:10.950
written our names in the Lamb's Book of

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:13.469
Life. It's

00:07:13.479 --> 00:07:16.150
Your blood that sets us free. By the blood of

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:18.150
the Lamb and by the word of our

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:20.830
testimony, we take this blood

00:07:20.840 --> 00:07:23.070
in the name of Jesus.

00:07:30.879 --> 00:07:33.670
We give You

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:39.029
praise,

00:07:39.039 --> 00:07:43.469
Father, for Your

00:07:43.479 --> 00:07:45.790
presence and the anointing of

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:50.029
the Holy

00:07:50.039 --> 00:07:54.390
Spirit. We love You and we magnify You.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.790
Happy

00:07:56.800 --> 00:08:00.350
birthday to You,

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:09.629
dear

00:08:09.639 --> 00:08:12.029
Jesus!

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:20.469
One day we'll celebrate His

00:08:20.479 --> 00:08:22.909
birthday with Him

00:08:22.919 --> 00:08:24.390
in

00:08:30.469 --> 00:08:30.479
person;

00:08:33.200 --> 00:08:36.670
I look forward to that.

00:08:49.920 --> 00:09:02.069
We honor the Lord today.

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:08.269
Thank You for all You've done

00:09:08.279 --> 00:09:11.630
for us this

00:09:11.640 --> 00:09:14.269
year. Thank You for President

00:09:14.279 --> 00:09:17.310
Trump and the new

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:20.389
administration coming in,

00:09:20.389 --> 00:09:20.399
giving

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:22.990
us another opportunity

00:09:22.990 --> 00:09:23.000
and

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:27.069
a season of

00:09:27.079 --> 00:09:29.630
grace.

00:09:29.640 --> 00:09:33.190
Sister

00:09:33.190 --> 00:09:33.200
Billye

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:35.110
talked about the gifts being

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:36.509
distributed on the

00:09:36.519 --> 00:09:38.870
25th, and we believe something supernatural

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:38.880
has

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:41.910
happened today. We

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:44.269
pray you felt His presence in your house

00:09:44.279 --> 00:09:46.509
today as you're spending time with your

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:48.590
loved

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:51.750
ones. Maybe you're alone, but you are not

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:53.990
alone because we are with you.

00:09:56.120 --> 00:09:58.110
If you don't have any

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:00.790
family, we are your family.

00:10:00.790 --> 00:10:00.800
Diana,

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:03.110
Braden, and I are loving on you

00:10:03.110 --> 00:10:03.120
through

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.350
the camera, telling you that you've

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.190
got what it takes.

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:09.870
Jesus has a plan for your

00:10:09.880 --> 00:10:12.829
life. You may feel alone

00:10:12.839 --> 00:10:15.069
in the natural, but

00:10:15.079 --> 00:10:17.389
there's somebody

00:10:17.399 --> 00:10:19.590
in a little house in

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:22.230
Oklahoma believing God with you.

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:29.710
2025 is going to be an amazing year

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:33.150
for you. Like we always

00:10:33.160 --> 00:10:35.389
say, Diana, put a smile on your face

00:10:35.399 --> 00:10:38.110
and a song on your heart.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:40.310
There are good days ahead for

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:42.790
the body of Christ. We

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:46.910
had a lady send us a

00:10:46.920 --> 00:10:49.470
letter. She

00:10:49.470 --> 00:10:49.480
is

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:51.430
alone, her husband has

00:10:51.430 --> 00:10:51.440
passed, and

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:54.350
her little canary

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:57.750
passed away recently. She's having a hard time,

00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:00.800
and

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:06.030
her letter

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:08.590
was so touching. There are so many people

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:11.870
going through so much right

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:15.750
now. Even the loss of a little bird matters;

00:11:15.750 --> 00:11:15.760
she wanted

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:18.030
to know if it

00:11:18.030 --> 00:11:18.040
would

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:19.710
be

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:21.389
in heaven because she

00:11:21.399 --> 00:11:25.990
misses her friend. I promised

00:11:25.990 --> 00:11:26.000
I wasn't

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.710
going to cry,

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:32.750
but it really touched me.

00:11:32.760 --> 00:11:35.150
William Branham talked about this before

00:11:35.160 --> 00:11:37.509
he went home to be with the Lord.

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.350
Sister Billye told us this story.

00:11:45.519 --> 00:11:49.269
If an animal was precious

00:11:49.279 --> 00:11:52.910
to you on this earth, God

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:56.230
has so much compassion

00:11:56.230 --> 00:11:56.240
and

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:58.949
love for us

00:11:58.959 --> 00:12:01.430
that those animals

00:12:01.430 --> 00:12:01.440
are

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:02.990
waiting

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:04.470
for you in heaven.

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:07.790
The Lord showed William

00:12:07.790 --> 00:12:07.800
Branham

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:10.069
that those animals, even

00:12:10.079 --> 00:12:11.910
during the Rapture, are so

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:14.110
important to you that they

00:12:14.110 --> 00:12:14.120
are

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:16.069
going to be taken too. He

00:12:16.079 --> 00:12:18.030
gives you the desires of your heart,

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:22.509
and if it's your desire to have your pet

00:12:22.519 --> 00:12:24.189
with

00:12:24.199 --> 00:12:25.750
you, the Lord's going to see to it.

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:33.470
He cares

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:37.310
about the smallest details

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:40.310
in your life.

00:12:47.839 --> 00:12:50.990
He has it all figured out.

00:12:55.800 --> 00:12:59.189
I believe the little

00:12:59.189 --> 00:12:59.199
parakeets,

00:12:59.199 --> 00:13:01.750
sparrows,

00:13:01.750 --> 00:13:01.760
and

00:13:01.760 --> 00:13:03.710
even a little 'Peanut

00:13:03.720 --> 00:13:06.230
the pocket squirrel'like Bob Ross

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:08.710
used to

00:13:08.710 --> 00:13:08.720
carry—God

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:11.710
cares about

00:13:14.269 --> 00:13:14.279
them.

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:20.949
I'll never forget when my dog

00:13:20.949 --> 00:13:20.959
died

00:13:20.959 --> 00:13:23.389
when

00:13:23.399 --> 00:13:25.230
I was

00:13:26.839 --> 00:13:29.949
Braden's age.

00:13:29.959 --> 00:13:31.829
It meant so much

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:33.710
to

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:37.269
me

00:13:37.269 --> 00:13:37.279
and

00:13:37.279 --> 00:13:40.110
hurt so bad at the time, but I gave it

00:13:40.110 --> 00:13:40.120
over to the

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:43.470
Lord.

00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:48.230
When I heard the testimony from

00:13:48.230 --> 00:13:48.240
Billye while

00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:49.750
we were sitting around

00:13:49.750 --> 00:13:49.760
the

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:51.550
table

00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:53.829
talking about the Rapture,

00:13:53.829 --> 00:13:53.839
we

00:13:53.839 --> 00:13:56.430
were

00:13:56.440 --> 00:13:58.790
all

00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:01.710
rejoicing over the fact

00:14:02.959 --> 00:14:05.389
that soon and very soon, we're

00:14:05.399 --> 00:14:07.389
about to go see the

00:14:07.399 --> 00:14:11.550
King. Our loved ones and our

00:14:11.560 --> 00:14:14.110
loved animals are going to come right

00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:17.509
alongside us.

00:14:17.519 --> 00:14:19.310
William

00:14:19.310 --> 00:14:19.320
Branham

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:21.230
saw many amazing things before he

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:23.509
went to be with the Lord.

00:14:30.360 --> 00:14:33.509
He

00:14:33.519 --> 00:14:35.710
even saw

00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:35.720
egg-shaped

00:14:35.720 --> 00:14:38.509
cars in the

00:14:38.509 --> 00:14:38.519
1940s and 50s

00:14:38.519 --> 00:14:40.710
that were driving themselves,

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:44.230
like

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:47.509
Teslas.

00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:49.389
He

